#* Marston
#*: As deer, being stuck, fly through many '''soils''', / Yet still the shaft sticks fast.
# Dung; compost; manure.
#: ''night '''soil'''''
#* Mortimer
#*: Improve land by dung and other sort of '''soils'''.

